== Introduction ==

This page provides an overview of the translatable KDE modules in Launchpad for Kubuntu Karmic and their correspondence with the upstream ones.

You can use the table provided to:

* match the KDE translations in Launchpad with the upstream ones and find out where to contribute back those from Launchpad
* fix translation bugs in Kubuntu, find the upstream location and report and send the fixes upstream

== Kubuntu and KDE versions ==

Kubuntu Jaunty was released with '''KDE 4.2.2''':

* <nowiki>[[http://techbase.kde.org/Schedules/KDE4/4.2_Release_Schedule|KDE 4.2 release schedule]]</nowiki>
* JauntyReleaseSchedule

== Translations list ==

'''Note:''' to go to the upstream file for your locale, after having clicked on the link from the '''KDE template''' column, you'll have to modify the URL for your locale. For example, if your locale is Hindi (hi), you'll have to modify the URL from the original link:

<pre>
http://websvn.kde.org/tags/KDE/4.2.2/kde-l10n/ca/messages/kdelibs/kio4.po?revision=HEAD&view=markup
</pre>

to

<pre>
http://websvn.kde.org/tags/KDE/4.2.2/kde-l10n/hi/messages/kdelibs/kio4.po?revision=HEAD&view=markup
</pre>

This is simply due to the fact that the SVN URL structure does not allow for providing a generic link for all locales.

The '''Notes''' column can be used to highlight any issues with the translation templates
